uk.co.corelogic.npa.common
[Groovy] Class CheckResult

java.lang.Object
  uk.co.corelogic.npa.common.CheckResult

class CheckResult
extends Object

A CheckResult is the result of a check. It is geared towards nagios checks. It isn't the same as a metric, and can contain the results of a check which uses one or more metrics.
